1.0.name: wordpress/shop-front
1.0.description: A Simple, responsive & easily extensible theme for the Easy Digital Downloads plugin. It also functions perfectly without the plugin as a standard WordPress blog. A free child theme for modifications can be downloaded from sumobi.com as well as other free and paid add-ons to enhance the functionality and styling.
